# Bitcoin Inheritance Protocol Configuration

## Testnet Configuration (Default)
# Network: Bitcoin Testnet
# RPC Host: localhost:18334
# Default Timelock: 180 days
# Default Fee: 2000 satoshis

## Mainnet Configuration
# Network: Bitcoin Mainnet  
# RPC Host: localhost:8334
# Default Timelock: 180 days
# Default Fee: 2000 satoshis

## To use this configuration:
# 1. Start btcd with testnet: btcd --testnet --rpcuser=testuser --rpcpass=testpass
# 2. Run the application: ./bitcoin-inheritance generate --testnet
# 3. Fund the generated P2WSH address from a testnet faucet

## Testnet Faucets:
# - https://testnet-faucet.mempool.co/
# - https://tbtc.bitaps.com/
# - https://bitcoinfaucet.uo1.net/
# - https://coinfaucet.eu/en/btc-testnet/

## btcd Configuration File (btcd.conf):
# [Application Options]
# testnet=1
# rpcuser=testuser
# rpcpass=testpass
# rpclisten=localhost:18334

## Security Notes:
# - Never use mainnet with this development version
# - Always use testnet for development and testing
# - Keep private keys secure
# - Use proper key management in production
